/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係自邨叫左「香港人」......全場靜曬，淨係聽到有個藍絲和應「垃圾」「廢青」同問候人娘親。<br />\n<br />\n「香港人！」<br />\n「...........................................」<br />\n<br />\n唉，心淡<br />\n我條邨，天水圍北，得五幢姐，正常地方細好應聲，結果靜英英。<br />\n<br />\n希望聽日有人係樓下同自己和應啦，無就以後都唔係屋企叫"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:25:19.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T15:36:58.000Z","msg":"Thank you <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:18:45.000Z","msg":"巴打 你唔嗌 就冇人應你<br />\n個個都咁諗就冇人嗌<br />\n希望你可以做帶頭個個<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1456c045b023b9fe59c1bc53850adf685ae908af","tid":1508442,"uid":23853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:20:37.000Z","msg":"有無人有天水圍大叫條片？"},{"pid":"73a30589622f0fe2c9c011736406bc5bc5f0f1e9","tid":1508442,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:21:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}